  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe will reimburse reasonable and necessary business expenses incurred by you while conducting authorized company business that are within the parameters of our complete Business \u0026nbsp;Expense Policy. All expenses must be legitimate, properly documented with receipts, and submitted in a timely manner according to company procedures.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThis policy ensures fair reimbursement for business-related costs while maintaining fiscal responsibility and compliance with internal controls and tax regulations. You are expected to exercise good judgment and prudence when incurring expenses on behalf of the Company.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
